text:
Mamimi, it's almost time to go on.
Are all your preparations complete?

This time, you've done great even though 
it's been so busy. Thank you.

Nah, like I said...
It wasn't like I tried that hard or anything...

And from here on out
I'll keep giving it a half-hearted effort.

Half-hearted huh... Haha...
Yeah, that's fine!

Go out there and give your best half-herted effor...!
I'll be cheering you on...!
